headline: 3 Ultra-High-Yield Dividend Stocks I Don't Plan on Ever Selling
summary: Ares Capital has delivered a long-term cumulative return that trounced the S&P 500.  Enterprise Products Partners is resilient and has better long-term prospects than many might think.  Verizon Communications has staying power and should be a key player in 6G wireless networks in the future.
